result.title: Good luck to all participants of the IOI 2015 in tomorrow's contest in Second round.
result.content:
Tomorrow is the second Contest day. It was held in (Contest hall, Al-Farabi Library).

The contest will begin at 09:00 and end 14:00.

On my own behalf and also on behalf of all participants (Codeforces) good luck mainly introduce to the participants that Russia as well as all the participants from other countries. Good luck (Michael Ipatov) and (Mikhail Putilin) that they have passed the second day of the Olympic with the result srl.

Link for results http://scoreboard.ioinformatics.org/Ranking.html and http://ioi.snarknews.info/index.cgi?data=2015/day2pre&class=ioi2015&year=2015.

Link about problems http://ioi2015.kz/content/view/1/271 .

After contest i propose to discuss the problem here.

Good luck to all participants of the IOI 2015 in tomorrow's contest in Second round.
